# Production Environment Variables

## Frontend (.env.production in Vercel)
VITE_API_URL=https://jeraisy-dns-production.up.railway.app
VITE_APP_ENV=production

## Backend (Environment Variables in Railway)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://[your-supabase-connection-string]
PORT=3000
JWT_SECRET=[generate-secure-random-key]
ACTIVE_CRM=oracle
ORACLE_API_URL=[oracle-crm-endpoint]
ORACLE_API_KEY=[oracle-api-key]

## Security Notes
- JWT_SECRET: Use a strong random key (256-bit)
- DATABASE_URL: Ensure SSL is enabled
- API Keys: Store securely, never in code
- CORS: Configure for production domain only